{"tid":287244,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"椰林閣 新界撚","createTime":"2017-06-17T09:12:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-17T09:45:44.000Z","uid":47866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fba92ff681ac506eb399150e56cb91920a091b87","tid":287244,"uid":47866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T09:12:54.000Z","msg":"對於我嚟講，椰林閣係一個好靜嘅地方<br />\n以前學生時代，大概08，07年<br />\n成日去椰林閣，一星期總有一兩日係去椰林閣<br />\n以前只要出大聲小小，全間餐廳就會聽到<br />\n坐近小小都會望著你嗰台發生咩事<br />\n所以我係好享受嗰一個寧靜的下午茶<br />\n但係元朗嗰兩間YLK唔知係邊年就倒閉咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n至此好小食YLK<br />\n直至今日去屯門廣場個間<br />\n但感覺完全唔同<br />\n好嘈，好多噪音，坐對面位講嘅野都聽得好辛苦<br />\n唔好以為今日係星期六所以有好多大陸撚先咁嘈<br />\n我係入面聽到大部分都係廣東話<br />\n感覺真條好差"},{"pid":"c45294952110c5ff6c59d4f152b5988dfba4da88","tid":287244,"uid":47866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T09:16:51.000Z","msg":"附上一張食物相<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/17/171423_f77e8df965d24a11a4e952096aa0a483.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F17%2F171423_f77e8df965d24a11a4e952096aa0a483.jpg&h=00e26881&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以前大概三十八，九就有一份下午茶<br />\n<br />\n而家四十二<br />\n<br />\n雖然價錢冇大變動，但質素差好多（可能今日星期六）"},{"pid":"be296d9e6aabd84369fb3196cffa08d8440033d9","tid":287244,"uid":118551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T09:20:30.000Z","msg":"以前係彩園成日食"},{"pid":"fafc9ca5a1269d21729308e8d3410f9d5ea23ddd","tid":287244,"uid":113546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T09:27:59.000Z","msg":"讀書果時好少去椰撚閣 窮丁丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後有去過幾次 但情況已經同樓主講既一樣 好嘈"},{"pid":"441bd6dd0de74bee1c54b3be6d3ad55c70db7c2b","tid":287244,"uid":20182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T09:30:48.000Z","msg":"間野不嬲都多負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 亞絲娜唔係公廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71fe569e9752c02f5b34e660edc79a16fc47007b","tid":287244,"uid":47866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T09:35:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前係彩園成日食</blockquote><br />\n利申 未食過其他YLK ,忠於元𨳒朗YLK"},{"pid":"d69ccdc7bc94c938d9379f4ead0ce01ecfa487d0","tid":287244,"uid":33721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T09:36:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>讀書果時好少去椰撚閣 窮丁丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後有去過幾次 但情況已經同樓主講既一樣 好嘈</blockquote><br />\n學生餐算抵食 食湯有包有野食"},{"pid":"26b0e4037dbd801456fba00e764b998899d9e0fc","tid":287244,"uid":33721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T09:36:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>讀書果時好少去椰撚閣 窮丁丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後有去過幾次 但情況已經同樓主講既一樣 好嘈</blockquote><br />\n學生餐算抵食 有湯有餐包有野飲  自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </blockquote>"},{"pid":"318418d54686e06cbcf654f92bbe1ee1eed281d6","tid":287244,"uid":47866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T09:37:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>讀書果時好少去椰撚閣 窮丁丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後有去過幾次 但情況已經同樓主講既一樣 好嘈</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我初中就較為常去，但係之後幾年都少了<br />\n今日食嘅時候，個friend講咩都聽唔清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c6e90015361823f442b80d747763ff044610be6","tid":287244,"uid":47866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T09:40:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>間野不嬲都多負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 亞絲娜唔係公廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n質素差咗好多，塊牛排係極難咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBetween 你講邊個亞絲娜先"},{"pid":"3115e17129088ac71973f5fdd7bdefff016f5f66","tid":287244,"uid":120660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T09:45:13.000Z","msg":"勁撚難食又貴<br />\n根本早就應該全線結業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe71859eacc944dffcefe4eb638d205d714b1c8","tid":287244,"uid":47866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T09:45:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>讀書果時好少去椰撚閣 窮丁丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後有去過幾次 但情況已經同樓主講既一樣 好嘈</blockquote><br />\n學生餐算抵食 有湯有餐包有野飲  自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實只要食物質素只要唔好太差就已經ok了<br />\n但係今時今日嘅YLK食物質同大快活早餐塊牛排一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}